*.swp

# Portal runtime/state (never commit)
**/private/request_log/*.ndjson
**/private/*.sqlite3
**/private/daemon_state/**
**/data/cache/**
**/data/queue/**
**/vault/**
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/secrets/**
**/state/**
# Operational + PII state: aws-csm mailbox profiles carry real board-member
# names/emails. The canonical store is the LIVE tree
# (/srv/webapps/mycite/<grantee>/private/.../aws-csm); deployed/ is a DR
# snapshot and must never be versioned (PII + operational drift).
deployed/*/private/utilities/tools/aws-csm/
# Contact-roster leaflets (per-entity YAML under site-core/contacts) hold real
# PII — names/emails/phones. The canonical store is the LIVE webapps tree; these
# files are runtime/untracked and must NEVER be versioned.
**/clients/_shared/site-core/contacts/*.contacts.yaml
*.contacts.yaml

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
